    "Rather than re-observing these fields, we constructed VIKING-quality data by selecting observations such that the total exposure time per pixel was at least as deep as in VIKING, and which contain paw-prints of similar seeing.",
    "The observation settings for UltraVISTA and VIDEO (and how many of such observations were selected to reach at least VIKING depth, ⟨N dither ⟩) are given in Table9.",
